      <description><![CDATA[ <h3>ParkShelf 1.1.0</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Native Liquid Glass — now on by default (macOS 26).</strong> The shelf adopts Apple’s Liquid Glass material out of the box on macOS 26. Prefer the previous look? Switch to Classic any time in Settings → Appearance, or try the more transparent “Clear” variant.</li>
  <li>Refinements and fixes throughout.</li>
</ul> ]]></description>
